SIMPLE: unearned
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unearned
<hw>Un*earned"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not earned; not
gained by labor or service.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Unearned increment</b></col> <fld>(Polit. Econ.)</fld>,
<cd>a increase in the value of land due to no labor or expenditure on
the part of the owner, but to natural causes, such as the increase of
population, the growth of a town in the vicinity, or the like. Some hold
that this should belong to the nation.</cd></cs><-- these days called
windfall profits -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unearth</ent>⟦br⟧
